You will be weak.

23
00:02:01,554 --> 00:02:04,114
If you feel nausea,
please use the sacks...

24
00:02:04,224 --> 00:02:06,215
JAKE:
Yeah, Tommy was the scientist.

25
00:02:06,326 --> 00:02:09,523
