Looks very bad on my report.

43
00:03:50,863 --> 00:03:53,957
Hell's Gate tower,
this is TAV 1-6 on approach.

44
00:03:54,067 --> 00:03:55,830
Crossing outer marker.
Mine is in sight.

45
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,405
JAKE:
One life ends,

46
00:04:36,109 --> 00:04:37,599
