71
00:06:19,779 --> 00:06:21,303
MAN 2:
Got it! Need them!

72
00:06:30,189 --> 00:06:32,555
QUARITCH:
You're not in Kansas anymore.

73
00:06:35,027 --> 00:06:38,895
You are on Pandora,
ladies and gentlemen.

74
00:06:38,998 --> 00:06:42,729
Respect that fact
every second of every day.

75
00:06:45,004 --> 00:06:46,596
If there is a hell,

76
00:06:47,407 --> 00:06:49,671
you might want to go there
for some R&R

77
