driver is matched to his own avatar,

127
00:09:40,046 --> 00:09:42,742
so that their nervous systems
are in tune,

128
00:09:43,182 --> 00:09:44,615
or something.

129
00:09:45,985 --> 00:09:48,453
Which is why they
offered me the gig,

130
00:09:48,554 --> 00:09:50,385
