134
00:09:59,865 --> 00:10:01,890
You know, what we see,
what we feel.

135
00:10:02,001 --> 00:10:03,059
It's all part
of the science.

136
00:10:03,169 --> 00:10:04,659
And good science
is good observation.

137
00:10:04,804 --> 00:10:07,170
