for the next 6 years.

138
00:10:07,273 --> 00:10:10,071
All right.
Whatever.

139
00:10:12,078 --> 00:10:13,670
So, uh...

140
00:10:14,780 --> 00:10:16,179
Well, here I am,

141
00:10:17,917 --> 00:10:19,350
doing science.

142
00:10:20,553 --> 00:10:22,020
MALE TECHNICIAN:
They're coming out!

143
